The paper deals with image identification using computer vision techniques, specifically the SIFT algorithm. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves evaluating the performance of the algorithm against different image distortions, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.MM (Multimedia), or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves calculating false and true positive rates, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
